cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for aligning bilingual word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves linear algebra and optimization techniques, which are common in the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which are common in the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves computer vision techniques for word alignment, which are common in the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision).
